# 2279 - echo
# Read all input and output exactly the same

# Read character into A
A<I

# If A is 0 (EOF), halt
# Otherwise output and continue
# We use memory to check if A is zero

# Set up lookup: mem[0] = 1 (flag to halt), others = 0
[0]<1

# Check if A is 0
B<[A]

# If B is 1, halt
Z<B

# Output A
O<A

# Loop continues automatically
